Source: Journal
Author: TAYLOR
Vol / Page: IV/148
Edition:
Quote: As we came through the woods one of my boys whistled to a little bird the miromiro or wren the least bird of this country and it actually flew into his clasped hands ... it is less then the English wren but much resembles it ...
